                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><xi:include href="../encodingdesc.xml" parse="xml"/></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_kʼældym" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>kʼældym</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>kʼældun</orth></form><sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>кривая сабля</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>crooked saber</q></abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>кривой кинжал</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>crooked dagger</q></abv:tr></sense></sense><abv:exampleGrp><abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor"><usg><lang/></usg><quote>læqwæn imæ raguztæj ma in kʼældunæj æ bærzæj niccavta</quote><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>юноша подкрался к нему и кривой саблей ударил в шею</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>the young man crept up to him and hit his neck with a crooked saber</q></abv:tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>II 103, 187%l35%l</biblScope></bibl></abv:example></abv:exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Из %ikʼæl%i + %idum%i, где %ikʼæl%i — усеченное <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kʼælos"/> ‘кривой’, a %idum%i = %idum(æg)%i ‘хвост’, см. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_dymæg"/> | %idumæg%i; буквально „(сабля) с изогнутым концом“. Из иронской формы %ikʼældym%i идет <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>kʼaldimi</w> <gloss><q>вид сабли</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Саба"/></bibl>).</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From %ikʼæl%i + %idum%i, where %ikʼæl%i is truncated <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kʼælos"/> ‘crooked’, and %idum%i = %idum(æg)%i ‘tail’, see <ref type="xr" target="#entry_dymæg"/> | %idumæg%i; literally “(saber) with a crooked tip”. <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>kʼaldimi</w> <gloss><q>saber type</q></gloss></mentioned> comes from Iron form %ikʼældym%i (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Саба"/></bibl>).</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>